                            <i class="fas fa-bullseye fa-3x text-primary mb-3"></i>
                            <h4>Our Mission</h4>
                            <p>To provide innovative, high-quality industrial tools and equipment that enhance productivity, safety, and efficiency in manufacturing processes worldwide.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
